This is my python project for a robot that can possibly mow the lawn dome days.

it consists of 

HARDWARE
- a raspberry pi 2 B+
- a raspberry pi camera
- a l298 motor controller
- a 11.1V LiPo battery
- a ultrasonic sensor SD04

SOFTWARE
- mosquitto MQTT broker
- some python daemons for the sensors
- a python daemon which controls the robot
